        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"276777\">Mike Shulman</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/232160-learning.3A-reading-.26-references/topic/teaching.20modules.20and.20homological.20algebra/near/406070820\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>de Rham cohomology using undergrad multivariable calculus is an interesting idea!</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Calculus-Cohomology-Rham-Characteristic-Classes/dp/0521589568\">From Calculus to Cohomology</a></p>",
        "id": 406082522,
